{"id":102,"name":"التكاثر","transliteration":"At-Takathur","translation":"竞赛富遮","type":"meccan","total_verses":8,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","translation":"竞赛富庶, 已使你们疏忽，","transliteration":"Alhakumu alttakathuru"},{"id":2,"text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","translation":"直到你们去游坟地。","transliteration":"Hatta zurtumu almaqabira"},{"id":3,"text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translation":"真的, 你们将来就知道了。","transliteration":"Kalla sawfa taAAlamoona"},{"id":4,"text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translation":"真的, 你们将来就知道了。","transliteration":"Thumma kalla sawfa taAAlamoona"},{"id":5,"text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translation":"真的, 假若你们有真知灼见, (你们必不疏忽)，","transliteration":"Kalla law taAAlamoona AAilma alyaqeeni"},{"id":6,"text":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","translation":"你们必定看见火狱，","transliteration":"Latarawunna aljaheema"},{"id":7,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translation":"然后，你们必亲眼看见它。","transliteration":"Thumma latarawunnaha AAayna alyaqeeni"},{"id":8,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","translation":"在那日，你们必为恩泽而被审问。","transliteration":"Thumma latusalunna yawmaithin AAani alnnaAAeemi"}]}
